1999;;Darkness Falls;;British;;Gerry Lively;;Sherilyn Fenn, Ray Winstone;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Darkness_Falls_(1999_film);;With his pregnant wife at death's door after a car crash, desperate husband John Barrett (Winstone) invades the home of Mark Driscoll (Dutton) and holds both Driscoll and his rich, neglected wife Sally (Fenn) hostage in order to understand the events that led to his wife ending up in a coma.